reviewText: Though dated the information presented remains pointed poignant and relevant in regards to the topic of the death of truth and the decline of culture in the US. Dennis and Ravi are amazing expositors.
bought for my mom--i am sure she loved it
I was very displeased with this material. It did nothing for my apologetics ammo and was just talking... Very surprised

Two disc set. First disc is the best.  Both these men make irrefutable arguments for belief in God. A scathing critique of the "modern" views held by university professors and the so called intellectual elite.
If you want to see two great orators talk about modern culture and it's decline then this is a must watch for you. Jeff Foxworthy, though he may seem like an odd choice, is the perfect moderator.
Everyone, should listen to this presentation. Unforgettable.
